<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="width:524px; margin:0 auto; padding:0;">
	<div style="border: 0; margin: 0;">
      <a href="http://www.ebtchef.com/"><img alt="Everything but the Chef Weekly Reminder" src="http://ebtchef.com/images-layout/email-header.gif" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;" /></a>
		<img alt="Simply delicious meals you can make" src="http://ebtchef.com/images-layout/email-header-food.gif" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />
	</div>
	<div style="margin:0 3px; padding: 15px 40px; text-align: left; border:1px solid #d7c59f; font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: .8em; color: #333; background-color: #fff; word-spacing: .25em; line-height: 1.3em;">    		<!-- greeting -->
        <p style="margin: 15px auto;">
            Dear <%= @user.first_name.capitalize %>,
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 15px auto;">
            Your free trial account with <b>Everything but the Chef</b> is about to expire.
            We hope you have taken advantage of the many benefits Chef offers
            its members. Planning, organizing and having a shopping list are
            half the battle when it comes to meal prep. Chef does all that for you!
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 15px auto;">
            Please go to <a href="http://www.ebtchef.com/">www.EbtChef.com</a> and login.
            You may go to "My Account" page in the "Members" section and fill in your
            billing information now. Or after your trial has expired, your login will take you
            directly to your account page. Updating your billing information within the next 
            few days will guarantee uninterrupted service.
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 15px auto;">
            Your credit card (or checking account) will be billed each month on the
            day you signed-up (e.g. if you sign up March 20th, you will be billed
            April 20th, etc.) Chef service is very affordable at just $4.95 a month.
            And now we are offering a year subscription for just $49.95
            (for more than a 15% savings).
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 15px auto;">
            Remember, Chef means variety--something new and different every week.
            What's on the menu for next week? Please sign up and find out!
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 15px auto;">
            Best to you in your family mealtime adventures!
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 15px auto;">
            <i>Chef</i>
        </p>
    </div>
      <p style="border: 0; margin: 0;"><img src="http://ebtchef.com/images-layout/email-footer.gif" alt="Everything but the Chef - Helping you make family memories one meal at a time!" style="margin: 0 auto;"></p>
  </div>
</div>